{"tid":1673313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂，入黎睇睇，我忍唔住啦","createTime":"2019-10-24T14:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T15:11:47.000Z","uid":122438,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7928f14bc66d4f28cc7e2b4536fee66ab303f2","tid":1673313,"uid":122438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都唔係好鐘意開po<br />\n但都係忍唔住<br />\n其實做乜野呢<br />\n呢幾日又屌加泰集會，又話去就乜乜乜<br />\n唔去就係乜乜乜<br />\n我明國際戰線都係重要<br />\n你地係咪忘記左<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山</span></span><br />\n我想講既係<br />\nFocus 番落去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\nmon po 狗，五毛狗，三毛狗見到你哋嘅加泰post<br />\n只會話你睇下班傻系內訌啦<br />\nFocus 番落去每星期六日既發夢活動啦好嘛<br />\n唔好再執著有去加泰同無去加泰既人係點<br />\n先解決我地自己面臨既問題<br />\n有去唔代表我地贏左<br />\n無去亦都唔代表就一定輸<br />\n但的知再係呢個不痛不癢嘅話題討論落去<br />\n成個運動就會開始散<br />\n你睇，中大校長都比人出信屌啦<br />\n咁佢重係咪中大校長？<br />\n佢會唔會突然唔夠資格做校長？<br />\n唔會，就好似而加你地去左集會同無去集會，<br />\n國際會唔會因為一個集會放棄支持你？<br />\n為左一個集會反而支持班狗？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">係唔會嫁</span></span><br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗!</span></span>"},{"pid":"fda070120f8415a84c581ac46595651a7e7a27fb","tid":1673313,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"有沒諗過事實上中共是好撚驚, 場運動升級做獨立運動？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/epKaJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/epKaJS</a>"},{"pid":"4b3adc1338d912162eeb0b9ba3e6bcd136da8a57","tid":1673313,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itbR4in.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitbR4in.jpg&h=bd7ae3e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"de1fceb37203aa89f0d7a790c77b08b348bea619","tid":16